683        builder.shippingInfo = template.getShippingInfo();
684        builder.completedAt = template.getCompletedAt();
685        builder.custom = template.getCustom();
686        builder.inventoryMode = template.getInventoryMode();
687        builder.taxRoundingMode = template.getTaxRoundingMode();
688        builder.taxCalculationMode = template.getTaxCalculationMode();
689        builder.origin = template.getOrigin();
690        builder.itemShippingAddresses = template.getItemShippingAddresses();
691        return builder;
692    }
